Glencore Prices Initial Public Offering at 530 Pence a Share

-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-05-19T06:02:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-19/glencore-prices-initial-public-offering-for-market-value-of-59-2-billion.html
Glencore International Plc, the Swiss
commodities trader, priced its shares at 530 pence apiece in an
initial public offering, giving it a market value of $59.2
billion, the company said today in a regulatory statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
